roviding a cone over `F ⋙ G` with cone point `X`, see\n`Functor.toStructuredArrowIsoToStructuredArrow`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/StructuredArrow/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Functor.toStructuredArrow","kind":"def","line":746,"name":"CategoryTheory.Functor.toStructuredArrow","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/StructuredArrow/Basic.lean#L746-L756"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Comma/StructuredArrow/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CostructuredArrow.IsUniversal.existsUnique\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">CostructuredArrow</span>.<span class=\"name\">IsUniversal</span>.<span class=\"name\">existsUnique</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">C</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u₁}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Category\">Category.{v₁, u₁}</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">D</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u₂}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Category\">Category.{v₂, u₂}</a> <span class=\"fn\">D</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">T</span> : <span class=\"fn\">D</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span cla